    <section class="about">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>We are a community-driven platform dedicated to reducing food waste while alleviating hunger. Our goal is simple – to make food donation easy, efficient, and accessible for everyone. Whether you're an individual with extra food, a business looking to contribute, or a community organization in need of food assistance, we’re here to help.</p>

        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>Our mission is to ensure that no food goes to waste while providing nutritious meals to those in need. Through collective action, we believe we can make a significant impact in combating hunger and food insecurity.</p>

        <h3>Core Values</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Compassion:</strong> We believe that everyone deserves access to food.</li>
            <li><strong>Community:</strong> We unite donors, recipients, and volunteers to support each other.</li>
            <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> We work to reduce food waste and create sustainable solutions to hunger.</li>
            <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We keep our processes clear and open to the public.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- How We Work Section -->
    <section class="how-it-works">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>We connect food donors (individuals, businesses, and organizations) with those who need food. The process is simple:</p>
        <div class="steps">
