                <h3>Step 1: Donate</h3>
                <p>Donate surplus food directly from your kitchen or business.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Step 2: Request</h3>
                <p>Request food if you're a food bank, shelter, or community organization.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Step 3: Volunteer</h3>
                <p>Help deliver food to those in need by joining our network of volunteers.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
